Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This should be the right way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:37.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kaga Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:39.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.67,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(299,314)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Lonely Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:47.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:52.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:55.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro odoru tomerarenai no
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:01:01.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naite waratte kimi to no kioku zutto wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:11.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hontou no jibun wa doko ni iru toka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:15.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Otona ni narutte taihen de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.04,0:01:18.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ima wa wasurete mo ii kana
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:21.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yoru ga matte iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:25.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro wo hazumase aeru toki wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:28.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hashagi mawareba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.25,0:01:32.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutaetai omoi ni ima
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:36.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kizuite shimaisou de
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:39.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kako to mirai osorete ite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:43.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Karappo no mama ja ugeokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:49.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tanoshimeba it's all right hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:56.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana koto zenbu wasurete kimi to issho ni odori akaseba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:03.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Motto suteki na jibun ni nareru sonna ki ga suru no
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:10.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Owaranai Golden Time gyutto chikazuku kimi to no kyori wa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:17.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukazu hanarezu mawari michi demo taisetsu ni shitai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:24.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week since I started college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga Kouko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:32.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who's that hottie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.05,0:02:34.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A first year named Kaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:36.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hear her parents are filthy rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What were you looking at on your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pictures of Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:51.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,These are all of Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:52.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:57.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuo and I have been together since we were this small.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:59.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kindergarten, elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:01.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,middle school, high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,cram school, and calligraphy school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.48,0:03:05.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We did everything together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:12.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuo and I have always been together, and we will be forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:13.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Takada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.69,0:03:16.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:21.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you get in touch with Mitsuo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He always runs away when he sees my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for him for half an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:35.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why we're attending the same university if he's going to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:39.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A-anyway, Kaga-san, have you already established your schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:41.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have first period?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sports science.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:45.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really? Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:49.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to take the same classes as Mitsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but he won't tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to use your phone again to...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:56.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mitsuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:03:59.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:05.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He got away from me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:08.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,L-listen, Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you need to chase him at full speed like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Takada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My name isn't Takada...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:16.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tanaka-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your hint is: it's two syllables.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Two syllables...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:26.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's your own name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.60,0:04:32.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if you figure out Mitsuo's schedule, will you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and his club!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:39.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you ask him about that yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did, I'm sure he wouldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:45.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know everything about Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:49.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know how he's living on his own, and what company he keeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.75,0:04:50.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to do it for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...in cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:11.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:18.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That girl's always wearing brand name stuff from head to toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents must be rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:35.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Some of you may not be familiar with the term "sports science."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.13,0:05:37.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sports science is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.37,0:05:42.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom made some nice choices!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:47.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this ramen and instant yakisoba!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure I can have these?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she told me to share them with my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:02.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko asked you for my schedule, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:04.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no! There's no way I'd tell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're avoiding Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.60,0:06:17.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I've seen Kaga-san here and there this past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't seem to have any friends yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:24.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She sits alone in her classes, and she never gets to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:30.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What... You're sympathizing with Kouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.75,0:06:31.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Attractive girls really do have it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:45.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what they do, as long as they put on a pretty face, everyone feels so bad for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even in high school, no one cared about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They all said the same things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Just be glad she's so hot.\NI'm jealous. I wish I were you."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They should put themselves in my shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:58.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I never said any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:04.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you not to ignore Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:11.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But feeling bad for Kaga-san is my choice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:19.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:25.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Me avoiding Kouko has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:31.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in us fighting over Kouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:33.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:34.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:36.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is something happening now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:39.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The film club's welcoming party.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:42.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:43.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.79,Dialogue6,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(328,225)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}GOLDENTIME{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see! You were in a film club in high school, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make a great club member!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:53.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be a cameraman?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Have you used one before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kinda out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just checking it out can't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:01.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, you came, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oka-san, you're in the film club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh? You two know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.62,0:08:15.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the same mandatory English class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:18.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't call me "Oka-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what people call my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.73,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(344,44)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Note: Okaa-san ( ) means "Mother" and sounds very similar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:20.73,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(106,72)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}to Oka-san ( )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, Oka... chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:26.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'll do!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:28.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:31.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel like joining the film club now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the upperclassmen seem nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:37.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I like to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:43.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was thinking of checking out a few other clubs before I decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:51.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, Yanagisawa-kun here has decided to join!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,New first years are totally welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a nice face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:08:58.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can be an actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.13,0:09:00.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan, you're in the film club?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:07.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Anyway, that pretty girl who was with Yana the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:08.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's already joined a club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she's chosen one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:22.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My senpai told me the club recruiters have a hard time talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Overpowering! Out of reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:28.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She has an aura like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:35.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you and Kaga-san would both join the film club, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:39.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yana-san is avoiding Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:44.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san seems to really like Yana-san, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yanagisawa-kun, do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:47.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't explain why, but that's youth for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be having fun, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're throwing a welcoming party, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't open that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:01.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond that door lies the realm of demons!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:02.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:05.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sao-chan of the tea club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:14.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's the film club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:16.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're throwing your own party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:22.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're the new student who drank our tea on the day of the entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.02,0:10:22.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from us now!\NCome party with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.09,0:10:25.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.95,0:10:27.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:29.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not joining the tea club!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Help me, Yana-san! Oka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:34.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:39.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get sucked in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,BANRI!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Go get the pitcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:00.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You, pour!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:02.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:05.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Serve up the fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I-immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Choose a location for the after-party!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:08.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,On my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.90,0:11:12.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Dance, dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}We're out of sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tea club bowling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Roll, roll, roll, roll...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:21.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You smell so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:26.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Drink up, drink up, drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:30.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:35.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wrestle with him! Sumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:36.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:36.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off, take it off, take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Put on your loincloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.36,0:11:43.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ready... fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:47.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Like I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:12.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I hate three-dimensional girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:15.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're all weird, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.60,0:12:18.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'm going to live in the world of 2D!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:23.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then from now on, you'll be 2D-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.60,0:12:27.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! Call me 2D-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:28.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:30.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's T-Tada Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:37.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I need to go back to the film club...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:43.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hang out with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We'll party all night long!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:51.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:04.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The number you are trying to reach is currently outside the service area or-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:14.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't get enough sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:23.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up going to five parties with the upperclassmen in the tea club...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:24.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:32.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going through the rear entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:38.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell her you were with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,O-okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:43.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Also, make sure you don't tell her\NI'm joining the film club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:46.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.12,0:13:50.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She waits for you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You could talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It may just be a ploy to get sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:02.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, no one knows what she'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:03.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can finally go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm with the social dance club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're a first year, right?\NHave you already chosen a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.90,0:14:35.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:36.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Join us, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, join our club!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,At least come check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:46.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this kid's joining the festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:48.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What, he's already been bought up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, have you already joined a club?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:53.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:54.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're Tada Banri-kun from first year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Thank you for saving me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.43,0:15:06.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's that club you mentioned earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The festival club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:11.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:14.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Its formal title is the Society for the\NCultural Study of Japanese Festivals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just wander around like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:22.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They pounce on defenseless first years immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:25.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I didn't get enough sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:27.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Should I go to the nurse's office with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're a really nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:38.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:48.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:52.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's alone again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:55.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,N-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:02.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san likes someone else, and she's from a wealthy family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You might say we're too different...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to hear all of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:17.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.07,0:16:18.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What a hottie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:23.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she the heiress of that famous major hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little out of our league.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:28.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she'd just ignore us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:32.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:35.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Um... Yamada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:37.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:38.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:41.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what you were doing by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:44.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you know where Mitsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:49.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you did, you wouldn't tell me, would you, Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Or have you changed your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:16:58.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:04.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So whose welcoming party are you going to today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you cheating on us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:08.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're throwing a party today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think I can do two days in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:19.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should just make up your mind and join the club!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, my butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:22.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You had someone with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you change your mind, text us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:40.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the tea club.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think their names are Sao-chan and Shi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:48.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, what do you think of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:49.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:53.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, how many clubs have tried to recruit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:55.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.37,0:17:56.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't count all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:59.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's true of all new students...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've had zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:05.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:09.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I only took this flyer because it was lying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:15.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why no one tries to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:19.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as though I'm interested in clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:24.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not with Mitsuo,\NI don't want to join any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:30.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We went to school and cram school together, and I can't imagine myself without Mitsuo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:35.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But since coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:41.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've become invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:47.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's like everyone around me is ignoring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:54.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really that strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:58.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that's why Mitsuo won't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:05.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is this an act to make me sympathize with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Or is she serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:18.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should try talking to not just\NYana-san, but to a lot of different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.95,0:19:20.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Try starting a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You might be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You could try going to the welcoming parties of various clubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:28.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in our club?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:37.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I had just stepped away from the booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:39.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We do all kinds of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:43.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We view flowers and drink in the spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:47.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,barbecue and drink in the summer, pick leaves and drink in the fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.65,0:19:51.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and snowboard and drink in the winter!\NIt's a laid-back club!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:55.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you're interested, there's a great cafe nearby.\NI can tell you more there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:59.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They serve cafe au lait in bowls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:00.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cafe au lait bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:02.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll pay, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:06.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, my bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.77,0:20:14.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:17.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't joined any clubs yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:20.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you should definitely join ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.75,0:20:23.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We get lots of information about lectures and exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:26.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And we have lots of alumni who can help you find work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:28.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I highly recommend it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:30.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll also get a lot of privileges if you join...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:34.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I'm from a different university.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:38.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to people from other universities is mentally stimulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:43.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Some questionable clubs won't let you quit once you join,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but we're not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:49.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, we hold our welcoming party at a seminar house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's three days and two nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:53.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We leave Saturday afternoon, get there in the evening, have dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and party!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we come back early on\NMonday morning, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:02.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We don't ask new students for money, so you can take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.12,0:21:05.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:07.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Meet us in front of the main entrance tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have tons of fun! Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:11.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:21.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she was really intense...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:26.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Trying stuff like this isn't so bad, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We can decide if we want to join later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:30.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:34.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We have this opportunity, and everything is an experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:40.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is as far as I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:43.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you tomorrow, Tada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:43.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.44,0:21:55.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She feels she's become invisible, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:18.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Katate ni wa amaku shita okiniiru no cafe latte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:23.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hohoenda shunkan ni koi no kaori
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:28.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kanpeki ni kimetai no cherry iro no one-piece
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:32.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sasayaka de tokimeite kimi e isogou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:35.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:37.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ki wo tsukete amai wana
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:39.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Sweets & Sweets Cherry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sasayaite ageru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:44.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}(Nee chotto doki doki)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:46.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aa machidoosii kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:50.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Donna egao de aeba ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.00,0:22:53.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty love, pretty love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:55.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ga itoshikute
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.70,0:22:58.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Under the sky, under sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.41,0:22:59.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Te wo tsunagou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:05.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sunao ni narenai sonna watashi no te wo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.38,0:23:10.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hippatte ite ne
